Linked Services:
----------------
Links your data store or external compute resource to Data Factory, It stores the connection information to the external resource.
it supports 100+ linked services.

Dataset:
-------------
Datafactory objects that points to a data linked service
Meatadata about the actual data
Describes for example data type,location and name of the data.

EX: A file has stored in Azure Blob Storage like specifying the file info
 like --> container_name : data-dump
           Path: export/movies_csv
           File_Type: csv
           Separator: comma

Activity:
-----------

Data Movement
Data Transformation
Control Activities 

